FBIS4-19672 "drweu077_o_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-077 Daily Report 20 Apr 1994 CYPRUS House President Meets Montenegrin Prime Minister House President Meets Montenegrin Prime Minister NC2004113794 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in Greek 1030 GMT 20 Apr 94 NC2004113794 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] House of Representatives President Alexis Galanos today received Montenegrin Prime Minister Milo Djukanovic and Deputy Prime Minister Rade Perovic, who have been in Cyprus since yesterday. Speaking after the meeting, Djukanovic said that Montenegro expects Cyprus' support in its efforts to find a solution to the Yugoslav problem. Galanos said that they discussed the situation in the Balkans and the danger to international peace from Turkish expansionism. He also said that they discussed some initiatives at the parliament level of some countries that have close and traditional relations, and religious ties.
